lead_paragraph: Jaime Nared had 16 points and 10 rebounds despite sitting out the entire fourth quarter as No. 22 Tennessee snapped a two-game skid with an 86-36 blowout of Tennessee State.

headline.print_headline: No. 22 Lady Vols Trounce Tennessee State 86-36 to End Skid
